{{ Legal }}

與[[爭議|爭議]]事項無關的證據<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.quimbee.com/keyterms/collateral-evidence |title = Collateral Evidence |author =  |date =  |publisher = Quimbee |language = en |accessdate = 2019-10-07 |quote = Definition: Evidence that does not relate to a matter at issue. |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191007150844/https://www.quimbee.com/keyterms/collateral-evidence |archive-date = 2019-10-07 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。在涉及[[契約|契約]]、[[遺囑|遺囑]]，或其他[[書面|書面]]時，旁證是指從其他來源取得的[[證據|證據]]，而非由這些[[文件|文件]]本身作為證據<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://lawyer.get.com.tw/Dic/DictionaryDetail.aspx?iDT=51224 |title = extrinsic evidence |author = parol evidence rule |date =  |publisher = 高點法律網 |language = zh-tw |accessdate = 2019-10-06 |quote = 指並非包含於協議、契約等文件中的、而是從其他來源所得的證據，如當事人的陳述、訂約時的情況等。旁證在一定情況下可被用來證明有關的書面文件。旁證也指未以合法方式在作出裁決的審判庭上提出的證據。 |archive-date = 2021-03-22 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210322192255/http://lawyer.get.com.tw/Dic/DictionaryDetail.aspx?iDT=51224 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

